            "text": {
                "type": "mrkdwn",
                "text": "*Instant Responses*\n\nAsk Astro uses natural language processing to understand customer queries and provide real-time responses, eliminating the need for customers to wait for human assistance.\n\n*Extensive Knowledge Base*\n\nAsk Astro is trained on a vast dataset, allowing it to answer a wide range of questions about Astronomer, Airflow, and Astro, including features, use cases, troubleshooting, and best practices.Seamless Integration: The chat bot is integrated directly into Slack, our popular collaboration platform, ensuring customers can access Ask Astro effortlessly within their existing workflow.\n\n*Intuitive User Experience*\n\nAsk Astro is designed with a user-friendly interface, making it easy for customers to interact with the chat bot and find the information they need quickly and efficiently.\n\n*Continuous Learning*\n\nThe LLM powering Ask Astro is constantly updated and fine-tuned based on customer interactions and feedback, ensuring improved accuracy and relevance over time."
